            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股再創新高 收升1609點或3.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場憧憬日本首相高市早苗解散眾議院提早大選，有利未來推進擴張性經濟政策，推動日股再創新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251118_GL_source_ap_Sanae_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251118_GL_source_ap_Sanae_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經平均指數今早最高曾衝上53814點，飆1879點，其後升幅雖然稍微收窄，但一直在高位徘徊；指數最後以53549點收市，仍漲1609點或3.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15578695-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%86%8d%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98-%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%871609%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%963-1",
